Dialogue: 0,0:00:17.50,0:00:21.93,LC中文FHD,,0,0,0,,如今你认为我写了成千上万首歌{\fad(0,500)}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:23.80,0:00:27.62,LC中文FHD,,0,0,0,,不过是心受伤后得到的才能{\fad(0,500)}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:27.83,0:00:33.92,LC中文FHD,,0,0,0,,但是每次提到你 话太多了说不完{\fad(0,500)}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:33.95,0:00:37.72,LC中文FHD,,0,0,0,,而且我永远也不知从何开始{\fad(0,500)}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:38.93,0:00:43.28,LC中文FHD,,0,0,0,,从那天起没人能替代你在我心中的位置{\fad(0,500)}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:44.26,0:00:48.93,LC中文FHD,,0,0,0,,没人能补充你留下的空缺{\fad(0,500)}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:49.33,0:00:54.58,LC中文FHD,,0,0,0,,我问我自己 还能再爱吗{\fad(0,500)}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:54.88,0:00:58.98,LC中文FHD,,0,0,0,,一个人能承受多少伤害{\fad(0,500)}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:00.04,0:01:05.53,LC中文FHD,,0,0,0,,又一次打击 又一次疼痛{\fad(0,500)}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:05.55,0:01:10.49,LC中文FHD,,0,0,0,,一个人能承受多少伤害{\fad(0,500)}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:10.64,0:01:15.44,LC中文FHD,,0,0,0,,又一种害怕不能被我抹去{\fad(0,500)}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:15.90,0:01:20.59,LC中文FHD,,0,0,0,,不过是想搞清一颗心能承受多少伤害{\fad(0,500)}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:21.28,0:01:25.88,LC中文FHD,,0,0,0,,现在你觉得我应该让你走{\fad(0,500)}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:26.66,0:01:31.56,LC中文FHD,,0,0,0,,这样我晚上就不会再梦到你{\fad(0,500)}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:31.98,0:01:37.29,LC中文FHD,,0,0,0,,但我就是不能放下你{\fad(0,500)}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:37.58,0:01:41.92,LC中文FHD,,0,0,0,,你怎能连打都不打一下就离开{\fad(0,500)}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:42.77,0:01:46.94,LC中文FHD,,0,0,0,,你从未说过的那些话萦绕在我心头{\fad(0,500)}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:47.97,0:01:53.01,LC中文FHD,,0,0,0,,你所做的则锋利得像把刀{\fad(0,500)}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:53.32,0:01:58.25,LC中文FHD,,0,0,0,,我问我自己你有没有考虑过我的感受{\fad(0,500)}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:58.60,0:02:03.05,LC中文FHD,,0,0,0,,当你慢慢回过神儿的时候{\fad(0,500)}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:03.89,0:02:09.44,LC中文FHD,,0,0,0,,又一次打击 又一次疼痛{\fad(0,500)}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:09.61,0:02:14.45,LC中文FHD,,0,0,0,,一个人能承受多少伤害{\fad(0,500)}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:14.66,0:02:19.92,LC中文FHD,,0,0,0,,天哪 又一个伤口{\fad(0,500)}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:19.97,0:02:24.56,LC中文FHD,,0,0,0,,一颗心能碎多少次{\fad(0,500)}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:25.28,0:02:29.74,LC中文FHD,,0,0,0,,现在你觉得我会拿起电话{\fad(0,500)}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:31.58,0:02:35.86,LC中文FHD,,0,0,0,,然后告诉你为啥我这么悲伤{\fad(0,500)}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:35.94,0:02:41.10,LC中文FHD,,0,0,0,,但是每次提到你 话太多了说不完{\fad(0,500)}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:41.70,0:02:45.22,LC中文FHD,,0,0,0,,听你说得太多了{\fad(0,500)}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:46.17,0:02:50.64,LC中文FHD,,0,0,0,,听你说得太多了{\fad(0,500)}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:51.10,0:03:02.18,LC中文FHD,,0,0,0,,听你说得太多了{\fad(0,500)}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:17.50,0:00:21.93,LC英文FHD,,0,0,0,,By now you'd think I'd write a million songs{\fad(0,500)}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:23.80,0:00:27.62,LC英文FHD,,0,0,0,,Gifts of a wounded heart{\fad(0,500)}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:27.83,0:00:33.92,LC英文FHD,,0,0,0,,But when it comes to you, there's too much to say{\fad(0,500)}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:33.95,0:00:37.72,LC英文FHD,,0,0,0,,And I never know where to start{\fad(0,500)}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:38.93,0:00:43.28,LC英文FHD,,0,0,0,,Since that day no one had taken your place{\fad(0,500)}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:44.26,0:00:48.93,LC英文FHD,,0,0,0,,No one can fill up the space you left behind{\fad(0,500)}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:49.33,0:00:54.58,LC英文FHD,,0,0,0,,I ask myself, could I ever love again?{\fad(0,500)}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:54.88,0:00:58.98,LC英文FHD,,0,0,0,,And bear another beating of this kind?{\fad(0,500)}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:00.04,0:01:05.53,LC英文FHD,,0,0,0,,Another strike, another ache{\fad(0,500)}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:05.55,0:01:10.49,LC英文FHD,,0,0,0,,How much hurt can one take?{\fad(0,500)}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:10.64,0:01:15.44,LC英文FHD,,0,0,0,,Another fear I cannot shake{\fad(0,500)}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:15.90,0:01:20.59,LC英文FHD,,0,0,0,,How many times can one heart break?{\fad(0,500)}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:21.28,0:01:25.88,LC英文FHD,,0,0,0,,By now you think I would let you go{\fad(0,500)}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:26.66,0:01:31.56,LC英文FHD,,0,0,0,,That I'd stop dreaming of you at night{\fad(0,500)}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:31.98,0:01:37.29,LC英文FHD,,0,0,0,,But I just can't stop thinking about{\fad(0,500)}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:37.58,0:01:41.92,LC英文FHD,,0,0,0,,How you walked away without a fight{\fad(0,500)}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:42.77,0:01:46.94,LC英文FHD,,0,0,0,,The words you never said they haunt me{\fad(0,500)}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:47.97,0:01:53.01,LC英文FHD,,0,0,0,,The one's you did were as sharp as a knife{\fad(0,500)}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:53.32,0:01:58.25,LC英文FHD,,0,0,0,,I ask myself if you ever thought of me{\fad(0,500)}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:58.60,0:02:03.05,LC英文FHD,,0,0,0,,While you were slowly coming back to life{\fad(0,500)}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:03.89,0:02:09.44,LC英文FHD,,0,0,0,,Another strike, another ache{\fad(0,500)}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:09.61,0:02:14.45,LC英文FHD,,0,0,0,,How much hurt can one take?{\fad(0,500)}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:14.66,0:02:19.92,LC英文FHD,,0,0,0,,Another scar, for heaven's sake{\fad(0,500)}
